{"body": "Just an observation,\r\n\r\nIf the browser does not accept cookies, as it's common in facebook canvas apps using IE6 and 7,\r\nyou may fall in a very simple problem, which is a session is assigned but the browser refuses it.\r\n\r\nUnless you actually meet the criteria or just refuse the user,\r\nat the moment of the first request, there's no way to be sure (might be) if the browser will ultimately accept the cookie or not.\r\n\r\nSo this might be an implication why not to solve this problem.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/12459477", "created_at": "2013-01-19T19:11:22Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8961#issuecomment-12459477", "updated_at": "2013-01-19T19:11:22Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8961, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/yakko", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/6d9bb5ee597f62dcbfc76f76e6772ff8?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F6a1964015e956fb5321ce3dacc45e47d.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6d9bb5ee597f62dcbfc76f76e6772ff8", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "yakko", "type": "User", "id": 335238, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/yakko/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523d60d7bd354364b9006513"}, "id": 12459477, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8961"}
